{"tid":1311773,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警方呼籲示威者停止使用暴力及盡快離開","createTime":"2019-07-13T10:40:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-13T11:02:54.000Z","uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"44d951e71080eb62edb12c2e77f9f002d2f741ad","tid":1311773,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T10:40:08.000Z","msg":"警方呼籲示威者停止使用暴力及盡快離開<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n　　一項公眾遊行活動於今日（七月十三日）下午在上水石湖墟附近舉行，主辦單位在約下午五時宣布遊行活動結束。警方在現場發現有示威者與其他人士發生爭執，但當警方介入時，有個別示威者嘗試衝擊警方。<br />\n　　 <br />\n　　另外警方發現在上水港鐵站附近，包括龍琛路、龍運街及新運路一帶，有人有預謀及大規模派發頭盔、眼罩等裝備，並拆毀路旁的鐵欄，及在附近以水馬及雜物堵塞道路。<br />\n　　 <br />\n　　警方呼籲示威者停止使用任何暴力並盡快離開，而其他市民亦應該和平離開，切勿參與任何違法行為。 <br />\n <br />\n完<br />\n2019年7月13日（星期六）<br />\n香港時間18時27分"},{"pid":"daa33dd6c826dcf34497497c37ce99dfd0f1f414","tid":1311773,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T10:40:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201907/13/P2019071300788.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F201907%2F13%2FP2019071300788.htm&d=ev%2BvVaAtQ3cORw7W3wlzWcRCHeky4xD%2FQbA%2BfbsvJuc%3D&h=5441d9b0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201907/13/P2019071300788.htm</a>"},{"pid":"d63598272f23d79bc49396b76f86813e922a5e5b","tid":1311773,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T10:41:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62a5f87a1f60536a873cae83a29d17a1ab4fc94b","tid":1311773,"uid":75959,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T10:42:10.000Z","msg":"［抗分化］共匪宜家玩緊老技倆，拉一派打一派<br />\n<br />\n共匪一貫手法，分化、滲透，然後拉籠一派打一派，政府有時會軟硬兼施，打下感情牌博同情，亦會派三毛做打手，屌/笑/鬧/玩膠嗰啲當然90%都係三毛，但亦都唔排除有真心膠中計信咗佢地一套，所謂拉一派打一派，群眾鬥群眾就係咁，要你自相殘殺，孤立主要敵人，然後共匪就可以輕鬆逐個擊破，2014年雨革因示威者內部分裂而亡，切記歷史教訓，無論如何都唔可以比三毛成功分化"},{"pid":"ecb133fe3ccde8ac34279aabd78a0ebfeff7d77e","tid":1311773,"uid":4050,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T10:42:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>［抗分化］共匪宜家玩緊老技倆，拉一派打一派</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n共匪一貫手法，分化、滲透，然後拉籠一派打一派，政府有時會軟硬兼施，打下感情牌博同情，亦會派三毛做打手，屌/笑/鬧/玩膠嗰啲當然90%都係三毛，但亦都唔排除有真心膠中計信咗佢地一套，所謂拉一派打一派，群眾鬥群眾就係咁，要你自相殘殺，孤立主要敵人，然後共匪就可以輕鬆逐個擊破，2014年雨革因示威者內部分裂而亡，切記歷史教訓，無論如何都唔可以比三毛成功分化"},{"pid":"6eb90d96e1858a08f1bb45b4ea45cd800d78745d","tid":1311773,"uid":255427,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T10:42:39.000Z","msg":"收皮啦警犬"},{"pid":"64f2f01339aa8abd6982e16bf051775fb81fb60d","tid":1311773,"uid":105976,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T10:42:52.000Z","msg":"惡人先告狀"},{"pid":"fa3a3dcfa51a29be434b0b382a8c86e34983cd99","tid":1311773,"uid":41404,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T10:43:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hkucampustv/videos/307812079966535/UzpfSTEwNzIzODgzNTU6Vks6MjkzNjM2NzQzMzA3MDk2OA/?sorting_setting=CHRONOLOGICAL\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhkucampustv%2Fvideos%2F307812079966535%2FUzpfSTEwNzIzODgzNTU6Vks6MjkzNjM2NzQzMzA3MDk2OA%2F%3Fsorting_setting%3DCHRONOLOGICAL&d=ev%2BvVaAtQ3cORw7W3wlzWcRCHeky4xD%2FQbA%2BfbsvJuc%3D&h=cba8a269\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hkucampustv/videos/307812079966535/UzpfSTEwNzIzODgzNTU6Vks6MjkzNjM2NzQzMzA3MDk2OA/?sorting_setting=CHRONOLOGICAL</a>"},{"pid":"24bbabd181054f06311f85c9650f4cf2066b8b99","tid":1311773,"uid":8745,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T10:44:08.000Z","msg":"只見警察打人"},{"pid":"4bc9433acb3b547c2b4f2cf06b9e95537a8b2e37","tid":1311773,"uid":161222,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T10:44:17.000Z","msg":"佢份新聞稿肯撚定要改<br />\n<br />\n個別人士衝擊？<br />\n<br />\n全世界影撚住你尻